### Test 1: Valid Drug and Plan for Carrier 1 (should PASS)
POST https://localhost:7080/rules/validate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "carrierId": 1,
  "featureName": "DrugValidation",
  "requestDate": "2025-01-15",
  "drugId": 123,
  "planId": 456
}

###

### Test 2: Valid Drug and Plan for Carrier 2 (should PASS)
POST https://localhost:7080/rules/validate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "carrierId": 2,
  "featureName": "DrugValidation",
  "requestDate": "2025-01-15",
  "drugId": 999,
  "planId": 777
}

###

### Test 3: Only required fields (should FAIL - missing optional fields)
POST https://localhost:7080/rules/validate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "carrierId": 1,
  "featureName": "DrugValidation",
  "requestDate": "2025-01-15"
}

