### Test 4: Bypass Drug ID 888 for Carrier 1 (should PASS)
POST https://localhost:7080/rules/validate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "carrierId": 1,
  "featureName": "DrugValidation",
  "requestDate": "2025-01-15",
  "drugId": 888,
  "planId": 456
}

###

### Test 5: No planId provided (should FAIL PlanCheck)
POST https://localhost:7080/rules/validate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "carrierId": 1,
  "featureName": "DrugValidation",
  "requestDate": "2025-01-15",
  "drugId": 123
}

